Epsilon Branding — License Summary
==================================

This repository uses a dual license:

- Art assets — anything under avatar/, social/, cli/, kit/, and any
  visual design embedded in README.md — are licensed under the
  Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License (CC BY 4.0).

- Everything else — docs/, the structure and prose of README.md, and
  any code added later — is licensed under the MIT License.

Both allow reuse with attribution. If you build on Epsilon:

1. Credit "Epsilon (amcheste-ai-agent)" as the source of the art.
2. Do not represent your own AI agent as "Epsilon" — create your own
   mark. The identity is personal; the pattern is shared.

